T1  - Digital inclusion, social participation and subjective well-being of rural middle-aged and older adults - Empirical analysis based on Chinese Social Survey data
AU  - Hu, Jiangwei
AU  - Zhang, Guocai
AU  - Xie, Fen
AU  - Li, Yanxuan
JO  - Acta Psychologica
